PrecisRegulations Amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS by rewording paragraphs 37(2)(d) and 38(a) in order to ensure that payments under a Supplemental Unemployment Benefit Plan are determined on the basis of the claimant's normal weekly earnings in the job covered by the plan, and by making other minor changes that will make it easier to conduct business on the Internet or to make direct-deposits.

precis:
Regulations Amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS by rewording
paragraphs 37(2)(d) and 38(a) in order to ensure that payments under a
Supplemental Unemployment Benefit Plan are determined on the basis of the
claimant's normal weekly earnings in the job covered by the plan, and by
making other minor changes that will make it easier to conduct business on
the Internet or to make direct-deposits.
